		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CIV_ARABIANS_DAWN">
			<Text>Great King Saudian, your subjects await your return[NEWLINE][NEWLINE]Your Wealth great and your people greater Saddle Arabia has been stiffied by a recent civil war where you triumphed over your brother. Now you and your wife rule the once again over the wealthy and powerful united Saddle Arabia, your people yearn to be protected againist more conflicts and to live freely and peacefully. The choice is yours now as to how you do this whether through the pen or through the sword. [NEWLINE][NEWLINE]Oh, King SAUDIAN, will you bring everlasting peace to your nation with your vast wealth or will you fund and army and bring your people ever greater glory?</Text>
