		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CIV5_ARABIANS_HEADING_1">
			<Text>Overview</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CIV5_ARABIANS_TEXT_1">
			<Text>The Saddle Arabs are a proud race of horses who inhabit lands far from equestria's borders. They often have dealt through trade and diplomacy than war and thus have created strong ties to many great nations. Despite their peace-loving ways their lands were ravaged by a bloody civil war started by Saudian's own brother. As a people they are proud and strong and excel at any buissness venture, which has allowed them to become one of the richest peoples in all the world.</Text>
		</Row>
